Tablet: Not required

System Requirements:

Sound Card: DirectX 9 compatible

Description:
Ittle Dew - Arcade style role-playing toy in The Binding of Isaac, with beautiful cartoon graphics, puzzles and excellent sense of humor!
You have in the form of the girl and her flying foxes roam the island and terrorize local residents, stealing their wealth.

GOG Bonus:
- Wallpapers
- Soundtrack
- Avatars
- Artworks
- Early Game Prototype
